<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,835,1003]" box="[225,1432,894,915]" pageId="12" pageNumber="519">Mesotibiae without sulcus at outer side; upper eye lobe connected to lower eye lobe by a single row of ommatidia..........</paragraph>
